column7: A detachable jacket for a bike seat includes:
having an upper cushioning portion formed with a plu
rality of cells filled with pressurized fluid in the cells for
a comfortable cushioning purpose for a bike driver
sitting on the bike seat, and a lower skirt portion con
nected with the upper cushioning portion and protrud
ing downwardly from the upper cushioning portion for
telescopically retaining the jacket on the bike seat,
whereby upon releasing of the jacket from the bike seat,
the jacket can be repeatedly washed or conveniently
